OL,3,CFour teenagers among eight more people
OL,4,Ccharged over violent disorder
OL,6,FEight more people - including four
OL,7,Fteenagers - have been charged in
OL,8,Frelation to the violent disorder that
OL,9,Fdescended onto the streets of
OL,10,FSouthampton following the murder of
OL,11,FHenry Nowak.
OL,13,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Police
OL,14,Fsaid an 18-year-old and three 19-year-
OL,15,Folds are among those facing charges,
OL,16,Fbringing the total number to 33.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
