OL,3,CFour teenagers among eight more people
OL,4,Ccharged over violent disorder
OL,6,FLast month, eleven Hampshire police
OL,7,Fofficers and a police dog were injured
OL,8,Fas missiles, including wheelie bins
OL,9,Fand chairs, were thrown during
OL,10,Fprotests organised in response to the
OL,11,Funiversity student's murder.
OL,13,FThe latest charges are as follows:
OL,15,FThe charges follow protests after
OL,16,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,17,Fwith a minimum of 21 years for the
OL,18,Fmurder of the 18-year-old in December.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
