OL,3,CFour teenagers among eight more people
OL,4,Ccharged over violent disorder
OL,6,FAnger erupted when police body-worn
OL,7,Fvideo was released showing Nowak being
OL,8,Fplaced in handcuffs moments before he
OL,9,Fbecame unconscious and subsequently
OL,10,Fdied.
OL,12,FTwo police officers called to the
OL,13,Fscene of Nowak's murder have since
OL,14,Fbeen placed under investigation for
OL,15,Fpotential gross misconduct.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
